channel.description:
Safe deposit
Why did i make a safe deposit?
- I was bored and had nothing to do. - Never have been made before. - I have an idea for it.
My idea for the Safe Deposit.
- Just use as a normal bank. - Only use for rich guys. - Could be used to buy special Clan wars armour and deposit in a clan bank. ( if someone can make the sprites and coding) * Example * U can buy 100 rune-sets but cannot been sold in normal shop or is tradeable to other people or dropable. it will only drop when other clan guy kills u and he is the only one who sees it and can take it and trade it to a special vendor at a safe spot at clan wars. - And people can use it for something else ofcourse
